A slideshow which contains three images along with left and right buttons. There are also 3 buttons on bottom to naviagate to any image directy.
The homepage shows mobile phones and laptops.
on clicking any item, a new page opens which shows product details and an "Add to cart" button. on clicking add to cart button, an alert says"item added".
there are three categories of items available. On clicking each button, shows its respective items to buy.
A next and previous button  is also available which works correctly.
there is no next button when the list ends up.
the footer shows some information about website and some contact information about the website.
